content.rendered:
We, at AMI are proud of the time, dedication, and willingness to advance our employees put into their careers. Dustin Dewey, Brandon Clarida, Andrew Roberts, Zackery Simon, Alex Potter, and Jordan Porter are the latest AMI Employees to earn their Michigan Department of Labor Journeyman Designation. Congratulations to you all!

URAMI.
